        <updateDate>2024-11-17T03:09:20Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;This bill requires U.S. Customs and Border Protection to ensure that the operating hours of all ports of entry located on the United States-Canada border are equal to or greater than the operating hours that were in place immediately before the declaration of the COVID-19 public health emergency.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
